KNOWN BUGS
==========

  The complete, up to date, list of known bugs in mathtex can always be
  found on the projects issue tracker at:
  http://code.google.com/p/mathtex/issues/list

  It is quite likely that popular issues will either have fixes, in the
  form of patches, or workarounds. Therefore it is always worth
  searching the issue tracker when you encounter a problem.